	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;The &amp;lsquo;Will to Win&amp;rsquo; campaign film captures the essence of determination, sacrifice, and resilience in women&amp;rsquo;s cricket.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
