	&lt;li&gt;WMO is headquartered&amp;nbsp;in &lt;strong&gt;Geneva, Switzerland.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The International Meteorological Organization (IMO), whose concept dates back &lt;strong&gt;to the Vienna International Meteorological Congress of 1873, &lt;/strong&gt;gave birth to the organisation.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The theme for 2022 is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Early Warning and Early Action.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
